  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Combine cheddar cheese, mayonnaise, sour cream, minced pickles, eggs, almond flour or keto-friendly sugar, salt, and black pepper in a mixing bowl. Mix well until smooth.",
